        `.gitignore`-aware tree tool written in Python.
        
        Example:
        
        ```
        3
        ```
        
        Output:
        
        ![](examples/3.png)
        
        ## Install
        
        ```
        pip3 install 3-py
        ```
        
        ### Compatibility
        
        If you are on Windows, install `colorama` in order to watch some colors.
        
